gw.api.util.phone

Class EntityPhoneMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.util.phone.EntityPhoneMapper

  • public class EntityPhoneMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    This class wraps the columns on an entity that represents a particular phone number. Each entity can contain multiple phone numbers. Each phone number will be represented by a PhoneColumnProperties object and the EntityPhoneMapper class will contain 1 or more PhoneColumnProperties objects in a List that can be accessed through getColumnList(). This is mainly used by the phone normalizer batch process.
